contactText: Just north of central Stockholm, a few meters from the Roslagsbana train and E18, you will find EdgePerformance. We have ample parking as well as short-term living accommodations nearby at Scandic Täby. Täby Centrum with restaurants and entertainment is within a short walk. Join us as an individual or ask about team memberships. Individual Membership: $650 per month, Team Memberships: contact us for more information.
